headline: Berkshire Hathaway Misses Projections As Abel Takes The Helm, Operating Earnings Down Nearly 25%
summary: On Saturday, Berkshire Hathaway reported fourth-quarter and full-year 2025 results that showed net earnings attributable to shareholders slipping to $66,968 million for the year from $88,995 million in 2024.
